  <entry>
    <title>php初级漏洞</title>
    <url>/2026/05/17/php%E5%88%9D%E7%BA%A7%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-is-numeric-漏洞应用"><a href="#1-is-numeric-漏洞应用" class="headerlink" title="1.is_numeric()漏洞应用"></a>1.is_numeric()漏洞应用</h1><h2 id="实例"><a href="#实例" class="headerlink" title="实例:"></a>实例:</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="line">$a = $_GET[&#x27;a&#x27;];</span><br><span class="line">if (is_numeric($a)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    exit();</span><br><span class="line">&#125; elseif ($a == 404) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;flag&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>直接把a构造成404无法得到flag,但是可以利用php的弱类型比较,引入URL编码(想要绕过可以在数字前面或者后面加上%0a %0b %0c %0d %09),从而解得flag</strong></p>
<h1 id="2-extract-漏洞"><a href="#2-extract-漏洞" class="headerlink" title="2.extract()漏洞"></a>2.extract()漏洞</h1><h2 id="实例1"><a href="#实例1" class="headerlink" title="实例1:"></a>实例1:</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$data = [&quot;name&quot; =&gt; &quot;Alice&quot;, &quot;age&quot; =&gt; 25];</span><br><span class="line">extract($data);</span><br><span class="line">echo $name;  // Alice</span><br><span class="line">echo $age;   // 25</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="实例2"><a href="#实例2" class="headerlink" title="实例2:"></a>实例2:</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// 模拟用户输入</span><br><span class="line">$_GET = [&quot;name&quot; =&gt; &quot;hacker&quot;, &quot;system&quot; =&gt; &quot;ls&quot;];</span><br><span class="line">extract($_GET);  // 危险！</span><br><span class="line">echo $name;      // hacker</span><br><span class="line">echo $system;    // ls（覆盖了系统变量）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>总结:extract() 就是把数组的 键变成变量名，值变成变量值。</strong></p>
<h1 id="3-php双精度漏洞"><a href="#3-php双精度漏洞" class="headerlink" title="3.php双精度漏洞"></a>3.php双精度漏洞</h1><p><em><strong>在php中(实际上在所有语言里),程序是不会把浮点数精确到最后一位的</strong></em></p>
<h2 id="实例-1"><a href="#实例-1" class="headerlink" title="实例:"></a>实例:</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$flag = &#x27;flag&#123;test&#125;&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">extract($_GET);</span><br><span class="line">if (strstr($num,&#x27;1&#x27;)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    die(&#x27;Out!&#x27;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">if($num==1)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    var_dump($flag);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>把$num构造成0.999999999999999即可(最好在小数点后16位?)</strong></p>
<h1 id="4-比较和类型转化漏洞"><a href="#4-比较和类型转化漏洞" class="headerlink" title="4.比较和类型转化漏洞"></a>4.比较和类型转化漏洞</h1><h2 id="php比较类型"><a href="#php比较类型" class="headerlink" title="php比较类型"></a>php比较类型</h2><ul>
<li><strong>PHP包换松散(&#x3D;&#x3D;)和严格(&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;)两种比较</strong></li>
<li><strong>松散只针对值的比较,严格同时针对值和类型的比较</strong><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">echo (123 == &quot;123&quot;)?1:0;</span><br><span class="line"># 返回：1</span><br><span class="line">echo (123 === &quot;123&quot;)?1:0;</span><br><span class="line"># 返回：0</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$id = intval(&quot;12312a&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">var_dump($id);</span><br><span class="line">输出：12312</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">intval() 是 PHP 的 转换为整数 函数</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">intval($value, $base);</span><br><span class="line">- $value - 要转换的值</span><br><span class="line">- $base - 可选，理解为n进制（默认 10）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">示例</span><br><span class="line">intval(&quot;42&quot;);        // 42</span><br><span class="line">intval(3.14);        // 3</span><br><span class="line">intval(&quot;100&quot;, 2);    // 4 (二进制 &quot;100&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">intval(&quot;0xFF&quot;, 16);   // 255 (十六进制)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="php类型转化"><a href="#php类型转化" class="headerlink" title="php类型转化"></a>php类型转化</h2><p><strong>在 PHP 中类型转换有一定的缺陷，如果一个 字符串 要转成数值类型，首先对字符串进行一个判断，如果字符串包含 e 、. 、E 则会作为 float 来取值，否则则为 int ，上述例子由于 a 没有包含任何东西，所以被当作 int 来处理了，这里要说明的是，如果字符串起始部分为 数值 ，则采用 起始的数值 ，否则一律为 0</strong></p>
<h2 id="实例-2"><a href="#实例-2" class="headerlink" title="实例"></a>实例</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="line">if(&quot;admin&quot;===$_GET[id]) </span><br><span class="line">//注意到这里是强比较,不仅比较值,而且比较类型</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  echo(&quot;&lt;p&gt;not allowed!&lt;/p&gt;&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">  exit();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$_GET[id] = urldecode($_GET[id]);</span><br><span class="line">if($_GET[id] == &quot;admin&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  echo &quot;&lt;p&gt;Access granted!&lt;/p&gt;&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">  echo &quot;&lt;p&gt;Key: xxxxxxx &lt;/p&gt;&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">?&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">把 admin 给 URL 编码一下即可:</span><br><span class="line">admin-&gt;%61%64%6d%69%6e</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">但是发现传进去的值会直接给 urldecode(php会自动解码一次)，为此再把编码后的 admin 再编码一遍:</span><br><span class="line">%61%64%6d%69%6e-&gt;%25%36%31%25%36%34%25%36%64%25%36%39%25%36%65</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">传参拿 Flag</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
